net.cnri.repository.memory

Class MemoryRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cnri.repository.AbstractRepository
      • net.cnri.repository.AbstractDirectRepository
        • net.cnri.repository.memory.MemoryRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DirectRepository, Repository

    public class MemoryRepository
extends AbstractDirectRepository
    A local Digital Object repository entirely in system memory. High performance, no persistence.
